timeline.message:
Adds steps to the run REST API

Adds a "steps" field to the
/application/v4/tenant/{tenant}/application/{application}/instance/{instance}/job/{jobtype}/run/{number}
REST API with the following structure:

  "steps": {
    "deployTester": {
      "status": "succeeded",
      "startMillis": 1577972067092
    },
    "deployReal": {
      "status": "succeeded",
      "startMillis": 1577972067092
    },
    ...
  }

